## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="15b52-115"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> Konstruktor inicjuje <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> właściwości.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15b52-115">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="15b52-116">Identyfikator musi być unikatowa w obrębie danej gramatyki.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15b52-116">The identifier must be unique within a given grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="15b52-117"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> Konstruktor wyrzuca <xref:System.FormatException> w następujących okolicznościach:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="15b52-117">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor throws a <xref:System.FormatException> in the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
